=========== Passives ===========
Aggressive: As a bonus action, the orc can move up to its speed toward a hostile creature that it can see
Gruumsh's Fury: The orc deals an extra 4 (1d8) damage when it hits with a weapon attack (included in the attack)
Battle Cry (1/day): As an action, each creature of the war chief's choice that is within 30 ft of it, can hear it, and not already affect by Battle Cry gain advantage on attack rolls until the start of the war chief's next turn. The war chief can then make one attack as a bonus action
